Package services

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ServiceClear
    Clears rows in tables in the database
    ServiceEvent
    Returns some or all events for a given user
    ServiceFill
    Fills tables in database with data.
    ServiceLoad
    Clears all data from the database and then loads all the data for a specific user into the database
    ServiceLogin
    Fulfills login requests for a specific user
    ServicePerson
    Retrieves data about a specific person with a specific ID
    ServiceRegister
    Fulfills register requests.
